<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔驚午夜響鈴咩，嘈撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fca8c01a6a43743a2f6e52af5e155671702bf1","tid":6352,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>響鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔驚午夜響鈴咩，嘈撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 你冇聽過手機響鈴黎留名咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fafd3d9509f266f8c74267978fdee6d20e3412","tid":6352,"uid":13617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"打邊爐唔落午餐肉不如唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18103c669121d3ed18b54c29ea0e4e4c7221e50","tid":6352,"uid":22081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"南記春卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b9d524f475869f85bf3824edf0f4b5a4c7946c","tid":6352,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"爐"},{"pid":"7fec9bb76104e01157bf563f243e4abb43647292","tid":6352,"uid":29031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"街買野"},{"pid":"561e29fb4e55381d87fb0a88396bc0b8bc39e9ec","tid":6352,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>響鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔驚午夜響鈴咩，嘈撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你真係好幽默<br />\n<br />\n我自問都算個ok幽默既人 但係你幽默感比我真係高十幾二十倍<br />\n<br />\n錯 應該係100倍先岩<br />\n<br />\n估唔到我係呢個post竟然見識到你既威力<br />\n<br />\n我真係笑到爆左肚 依家一路打字一路撿返d腸呀內臟呀腎呀<br />\n<br />\n塞返落個肚到<br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過未來幾個月去紅館開棟篤笑?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec5437b377d4be21f8b756dc226a08da6e94293","tid":6352,"uid":22743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打邊爐唔落午餐肉不如唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實乜真係咁好食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得太淋太油但冇油香個隻 都係煎香佢好啲 脆脆地 加 啲油香啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw 打邊爐 臨尾都會加個烏冬 再加啲醬料e.g. 豉油 炸蒜 生蒜 蔥花 混合物黎撈 一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5633dfdc46da3dd10cd4649102ac820307bf06ae","tid":6352,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:00:08.000Z","msg":"山根"},{"pid":"b8047feddece7bd527b966f82b213c9d240fe50f","tid":6352,"uid":15569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"一定係響鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}